2000-04-30 21:08:36  bcox  <bcox@users.sourceforce.net>

	* /cvsroot/GGZ/ggz/ggz/Makefile.am, /cvsroot/GGZ/ggz/ggz/dlg_about.c, /cvsroot/GGZ/ggz/ggz/dlg_details.c, /cvsroot/GGZ/ggz/ggz/dlg_error.c, /cvsroot/GGZ/ggz/ggz/dlg_exit.c, /cvsroot/GGZ/ggz/ggz/dlg_launch.c, /cvsroot/GGZ/ggz/ggz/dlg_login.c, /cvsroot/GGZ/ggz/ggz/dlg_main.c, /cvsroot/GGZ/ggz/ggz/dlg_motd.c, /cvsroot/GGZ/ggz/ggz/dlg_msgbox.c, /cvsroot/GGZ/ggz/ggz/dlg_props.c, /cvsroot/GGZ/ggz/ggz/main.c, /cvsroot/GGZ/ggz/ggz/mnu_players.c, /cvsroot/GGZ/ggz/ggz/mnu_tables.c, /cvsroot/GGZ/ggz/ggz/support.h, /cvsroot/GGZ/ggz/.cvsignore, /cvsroot/GGZ/ggz/Makefile.am, /cvsroot/GGZ/ggz/acconfig.h, /cvsroot/GGZ/ggz/configure.in:
	This large commit contains all of the necessary updates to enable i18n
	support within the client.

	- Most UI strings are now marked as translatable.
	- Pre-processor directives have been added to support.h to
	  disable/enable localization based upon ENABLE_NLS.
	- The files for autoconf, autogen and family have had gettext support
	  added.

